name: Image Innovation
body:
### Image Innovation
This site is the home of various projects that I have completed that I'm offering as open source solutions. They range from serious projects such as Joomla! add-ins to Minecraft mods.

Browse the [repositories](https://github.com/imageinnova) and enjoy. If you would like to contribute to any of the projects, please send a pull request with your changes.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
